title: #123: Watchdogs Didn't Bark With John Duffy and Ray Nowosielski
description: It's time for the 2nd annual "Never Forget Never Again" Sept 11th episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This episode Sam welcomes the authors of "The Watchdogs Didn't Bark: The CIA, NSA And The Crimes Of The War Terror," John Duffy and Ray Nowosielski, to discuss the epic failures of the US Intelligence Community leading up to 9/11! This was an incredibly interesting discussion about one of the most tragic days in US history.  Thank you so much for your support.  Hope to see you soon at live upcoming event!
